---
layout: base
title: "Submit a Quote"
description: Know a great freethought quote? Submit it for our curated collection.
permalink: /quotes/submit/
---

<div class="container" style="padding-top: var(--space-10); padding-bottom: var(--space-20);">
  <div class="container--prose">

    <header style="margin-bottom: var(--space-10); padding-bottom: var(--space-6); border-bottom: 3px solid var(--color-ink);">
      <nav style="font-family:var(--font-ui);font-size:var(--text-xs);color:var(--color-ink-faint);margin-bottom:var(--space-4);">
        <a href="/quotes/" style="color:var(--color-link);">Quotes</a> &rarr; Submit a Quote
      </nav>
      <h1 style="font-family: var(--font-masthead); font-size: clamp(1.8rem, 5vw, 3.815rem); margin-bottom: var(--space-4);">Submit a Quote</h1>
      <p style="font-family: var(--font-body); font-size: var(--text-lg); color: var(--color-ink-muted); line-height: var(--leading-loose); max-width: 60ch;">
        Know a great quote from the freethought tradition? We'd love to add it to our <a href="/quotes/">collection</a>.
      </p>
    </header>

    <div class="article-body">

      <p>We look for quotes that are well-sourced, thought-provoking, and relevant to the freethought tradition — reason, secularism, science, liberty of conscience, and the examined life. Please verify the attribution before submitting. You can also email quote suggestions to <a href="mailto:{{ site.email }}">{{ site.email }}</a>.</p>

      <form action="https://api.web3forms.com/submit" method="POST" class="w3f" style="margin: var(--space-6) 0;">
        <input type="hidden" name="access_key" value="{{ site.forms.accessKey }}">
        <input type="hidden" name="subject" value="Quote submission — {{ site.title }}">
        <input type="hidden" name="redirect" value="{{ site.url }}/thank-you/">
        <input type="hidden" name="from_name" value="{{ site.title }} Quote Form">
        <input type="checkbox" name="botcheck" class="visually-hidden" style="display:none" tabindex="-1" autocomplete="off">

        <div class="w3f__group">
          <label class="w3f__label" for="quote-text">The quote <span class="w3f__required">*</span></label>
          <span class="w3f__hint" id="quote-text-hint">The exact text of the quote. Please use the original wording, not a paraphrase.</span>
          <textarea class="w3f__textarea" name="quote" id="quote-text" rows="4" required aria-required="true" aria-describedby="quote-text-hint" maxlength="2000"></textarea>
        </div>

        <div class="w3f__row">
          <div class="w3f__group">
            <label class="w3f__label" for="quote-author">Author <span class="w3f__required">*</span></label>
            <input class="w3f__input" type="text" name="author" id="quote-author" required aria-required="true" placeholder="e.g. Carl Sagan">
          </div>
          <div class="w3f__group">
            <label class="w3f__label" for="quote-source">Source <span class="w3f__optional">(optional)</span></label>
            <span class="w3f__hint" id="quote-source-hint">Book, speech, interview, letter, etc.</span>
            <input class="w3f__input" type="text" name="source" id="quote-source" aria-describedby="quote-source-hint" placeholder="e.g. The Demon-Haunted World, 1995">
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="w3f__group">
          <label class="w3f__label" for="quote-context">Context or notes <span class="w3f__optional">(optional)</span></label>
          <span class="w3f__hint" id="quote-context-hint">Why is this quote significant? Any relevant context about when or why it was said?</span>
          <textarea class="w3f__textarea" name="context" id="quote-context" rows="3" aria-describedby="quote-context-hint" maxlength="1000"></textarea>
        </div>

        <div class="w3f__row">
          <div class="w3f__group">
            <label class="w3f__label" for="quote-name">Your name <span class="w3f__optional">(optional)</span></label>
            <input class="w3f__input" type="text" name="name" id="quote-name" autocomplete="name">
          </div>
          <div class="w3f__group">
            <label class="w3f__label" for="quote-email">Email <span class="w3f__optional">(optional — if you'd like credit)</span></label>
            <input class="w3f__input" type="email" name="email" id="quote-email" autocomplete="email">
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="h-captcha" data-captcha="true"></div>
        <button type="submit" class="w3f__submit">Submit Quote</button>
        <p class="w3f__privacy">We verify all quotes before adding them. Misattributed or fabricated quotes will not be published.</p>
      </form>

    </div>
  </div>
</div>
